<p>Hi there</p>

<p>Your Pagecord is set up — now it's time for your first page or post!</p>

<p>You could start with:</p>

<ul>
  <li>A Home page: a welcome message, a bio, maybe a photo</li>
  <li>An About page: who you are, what the blog is about</li>
  <li>A first post: a recent photo, your thoughts on a film you watched, or anything else you'd like to share!</li>
</ul>

